::Zardus::

Zardus nods, looking from Stranato to Inzola. "We'll kill him next attack."

He looks at Wheeljack. "I have to give these two quarters, I'll be back."

Zardus turns back to Stranato. "Follow me, I'll assign you two quarters," he 
says, turning around to walk into the Alliance base, "For now, you'll get 
used to the base, then you can do whatever you want, as long as you're 
following orders."
